OL,7,FA special school in Bristol which
OL,8,Fhelps transform the lives of children
OL,9,Fwith autism has been shortlisted as
OL,10,Fone of the world's best for overcoming
OL,11,Fadversity.
OL,13,FVenturers' Academy in Withywood has
OL,14,F250 students who all have a primary
OL,15,Fdiagnosis of autism.
OL,17,FIt has been named in the top ten for a
OL,18,Fglobal award, by T4 Education, with
OL,19,Fthe winner due to be announced in
OL,20,FNovember subject to a public vote.
