OL,7,FJudges commended the school for its
OL,8,Ftailored educational experiences and
OL,9,Ftrips, its inclusive environment and
OL,10,Fits support out of term time for
OL,11,Fstruggling families.
OL,13,FAt an assembly, teachers told students
OL,14,Fabout the award which saw many jumping
OL,15,Fwith excitement. Headteacher Trystan
OL,16,FWilliams says it was a special moment.
