OL,7,FHe added: "The vast majority of our
OL,8,Fchildren live in the lowest 1% of
OL,9,Fpoverty. The children have an
OL,10,Feducation health and care plan. Their
OL,11,Fparents have fought and battled to get
OL,12,Fthem into a special school like this.
OL,13,FTo be globally recognised that our
OL,14,Fchildren are overcoming adversity
OL,15,Fafter covid, lockdown and lack of
OL,16,Ffunding - this makes it all
OL,17,Fworthwhile."
