OL,7,FParent Shaun Calloway told ITV News
OL,8,Fhow the school had provided a lifeline
OL,9,Ffor his family and his two boys with
OL,10,Fautism.
OL,12,FHe said: "The news about the award
OL,13,Freally made me emotional because I
OL,14,Fknow from personal experience the
OL,15,Fdifference this school makes to me and
OL,16,Fmy family. It is brilliant to be
OL,17,Fhonest."
